@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.24 - v2 + 0.03) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.76)) - wp.exp((v2 + 0.25 * v0 + 0.94)))
    v1 = wp.sin((0.83 + (v0 + 0.01 + v0 + 0.75)))
    tmp = ((v1 + wp.sin(v2 + 0.28)) * 0.86)
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.exp(tmp + 0.45) + (v0 + 0.49 + v2 + 0.43)))
    data[tid] = v0
